      <h2 id="condolence-messages-for-a-friend-who-lost-her-father-words-of-comfort">Condolence Messages for a Friend Who Lost Her Father: Words of Comfort</h2>
      <p></p>

<p>
  Looking for more Thanksgiving message ideas? Check out our guides for 
